<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home | Mandvi's Web App</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #23a6d5, #23d5ab, #e73c7e, #ee7752);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 10s ease infinite;
        }
        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
            50% {background-position: 100% 50%;}
            100% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
        }
        header {
            background: #2d3e50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2rem 0 1.2rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(35,166,213,0.08);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s;
        }
        .hero-icon {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #23a6d5;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0);}
            50% { transform: translateY(-18px);}
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);}
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0);}
        }
        .hero-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
            color: #2d3e50;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(35,166,213,0.08);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .hero-desc {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 1.7rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 440px;
        }
        main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .actions {
            margin-top: 2.2rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }
        .actions a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #23a6d5 0%, #23d5ab 100%);
            padding: 0.9rem 2.2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(35,166,213,0.10);
            transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }
        .actions a:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #23d5ab 0%, #23a6d5 100%);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.06);
        }
        .box-shadow {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 0 1.5px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 2.2rem 2.7rem;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1.2rem 0 1.1rem 0;
            background: #f0f2f5;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Mandvi's Web App</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-icon">ðŸš€</div>
            <div class="hero-title">Join the Future of Productivity!</div>
            <div class="hero-desc">
                Discover a simple and secure way to manage your tasks and connect with others. Sign up now and be part of our growing community!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="actions box-shadow">
            <a href="/signup">Sign Up Free</a>
            <a href="/signin">Sign In</a>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Mandvi's Web App. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
